<note n="0466002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466002">〔月喻…十六〕十二字－【甲】</note>
<note n="0466003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466003">到＝倒【甲】</note>
<note n="0466004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466004">白＝曰【甲】</note>
<note n="0466005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0466005">遍＝偏【甲】</note>
